FY_VIRTUAL_V2 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
A remake of my previous map.

Consists of only 4 main textures,
- Concrete
- Neon
- Glass
- Water

Cyan Neon throughout,
-A small/medium sized map,
--Two buyzones,
---Teams oppisite side,
----A base in the center of the map,
-----Can be entered underneath or ontop,
------Two ramps each side leading to a catwalk.

Komaokc's Skybox Texture.
TopHATTwaffle Waterfall Texture.

Some members of Steamgamers helped Beta Test.
Chicken McFail and Whazaaaaa helped by giving me ideas based on the map.
